              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl"><span class="text-red-700 dark:text-red-200"></span><a href="/books/fb5772bc-c0be-407f-bc94-46a3b282fc9c">The Language of Thorns: Midnight Tales and Dangerous Magic</a>
              
              
                <p class="font-semibold hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500 text-sm"><a href="/series/1175223">Grishaverse</a> <a href="/series/1175223">#0.5</a></p>

              <p class="font-body mb-1 mt-1 md:mt-0 text-sm text-darkerGrey dark:text-lightGrey font-normal">
              <a class="hover:text-cyan-700, dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/b0cf2339-a147-4668-a78f-d9bec0477450">Leigh Bardugo</a>
                <span class="hidden contributor-names">
                  with <a class="hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500" href="/authors/d66f7eea-f40b-4c14-89e5-fef9dee8bc0f">Sara Kipin</a> (Illustrator)
                </span>
              </p>
            </div>
            <p class='text-xs font-light text-darkestGrey dark:text-grey mt-1'>
            304 pages <span><span class="text-darkerGrey dark:text-grey"> • </span> <span class="toggle-edition-info-link underline decoration-darkerGrey dark:decoration-lightGrey cursor-pointer hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500 hover:decoration-cyan-700 dark:hover:decoration-cyan-500" data-book-id=fb5772bc-c0be-407f-bc94-46a3b282fc9c>first pub 2017</span></span>  (<a class="browse-editions-link text-xs text-darkestGrey dark:text-grey cursor-pointer font-light hover:text-cyan-700 dark:hover:text-cyan-500 underline decoration-darkerGrey dark:decoration-lightGrey hover:decoration-cyan-700 dark:hover:decoration-cyan-500 mt-1 pb-1" href="/books/fb5772bc-c0be-407f-bc94-46a3b282fc9c/editions">editions</a>) 
                        </p>
            <div class="hidden edition-info mt-3" data-book-id=fb5772bc-c0be-407f-bc94-46a3b282fc9c>
              <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-semibold">ISBN/UID:</span>  9781250122537</p>
              <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-semibold">Format:</span> Digital</p>
              <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-semibold">Language:</span> English</p>
              <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-semibold">Publisher:</span> Imprint</p>
              <p class="text-xs"><span class="font-semibold">Publication date:</span> 26 September 2017</p>
            </div>
            
              <div class="book-pane-tag-section mt-3 mb-4" data-bookid=fb5772bc-c0be-407f-bc94-46a3b282fc9c>
